          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1650389379640-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Fable pulled mushrooms </strong>to the dish</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1650389404380-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1650389404380-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1650389404380-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1650389404380-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1650389404380-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> to the dish with the <strong>chopped carrot</strong>, <strong>crushed garlic </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Add your<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>,<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> and 450ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [675ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[900ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat – this is your <strong>spicy tomato ragù</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1650389410620-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1650389410620-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1650389410620-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1650389410620-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1650389410620-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 20 min or until everything's beginning to soften</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1650389418198-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1650389418198-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1650389418198-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1650389418198-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1650389418198-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the spicy tomato ragù has been cooking for 20 min, remove the dish from the oven, season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good stir</p><p>Add your <strong>conchiglie </strong>and mix it all together so that the pasta is nestled into the sauce</p><p>Cover with a lid and return the dish to the oven for 25 min or until the pasta is cooked through – this is your <strong>all-in-one spicy Fable mushroom pasta</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1650389423594-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1650389423594-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1650389423594-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1650389423594-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1650389423594-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> all-in-one spicy Fable mushroom pasta </strong>topped with your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Tear your <strong>mint leaves</strong> over the top</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
      "order": 8,
